<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1991106-why-is-it-that-intellectuals-may-influence">Why is it that intellectuals may influence us with their ability to use the language, but when it comes to the practical application of their ideas, they often fail so horribly? They are also so often scumbags in their private lives. Paul&#39;s take on these folks is an essential read.</a>
</div>
